How to Use the Code
Running the Application:
The application can be executed using the command:

python main.py

Input Parameters:
The application accepts several command-line arguments:
--input: The path to the input file or directory.
--config: (Optional) The path to the configuration file.
--verbose: Enable verbose output for debugging purposes.

python main.py --input data/input_file.txt --config config/settings.yaml --verbose

Output:
The processed results will be output to the console or saved to a specified output directory 
(as configured in your settings). Check the documentation in the docs/ folder for detailed output formats and file structures.

For more detailed usage instructions, troubleshooting tips, and examples, please refer to the Project Wiki(To be created).
